summary:
Chidinma is a highly committed, self motivated and proactive self taught Software Engineer. She is a team player with outstanding analytical, technical and communication skills. She is also great at working independently.

Chidinma is a very curious person with a knack for finding out the hows and whys. 
She is excited about technology especially Deep learning, Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning.
